{"tid":267674,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam][普天同慶五週年]Ball3D: Soccer Online","createTime":"2017-06-02T12:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T16:29:38.000Z","uid":59491,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3802db788ecf29d52082be78cf8ca94cacb95737","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.ball3d.com/images/logo-ball3d.png?nowe2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ball3d.com%2Fimages%2Flogo-ball3d.png%3Fnowe2&h=1c6cbaa8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Ball3D: Soccer Online，由一名波蘭人Mariusz Kowalczyk (Maniek) 開發嘅第一身3D足球遊戲，每名玩家各自操控一個圓形人仔比賽。<br />\n傳、停、帶、射定用腳趾尾拉西同七旋斬都由你話事。<br />\n<br />\n你嘅足球哲學係以個人能力帶領隊友爭勝定重視團隊配合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想好似李斯特城咁打防守反擊定好似巴塞咁打tiki taka？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論點，你都可以係度實踐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家隻Game終於到咗第5週年，同埋順利上到Steam了。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">官方網站及遊戲下載：<a href=\"http://www.ball3d.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ball3d.com&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=94c51dea\" target=\"_blank\">www.ball3d.com</a><br />\n或上Steam search <span style=\"color: red;\">Ball3D: Soccer Online</span>下載<br />\n<br />\nBall3D: Soccer Online Facebook page :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ball3dgame/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fball3dgame%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f6adf228\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ball3dgame/?fref=ts</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港ball3d聯賽網 : <a href=\"http://ball3dhkleague.wixsite.com/b3dhk2016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fball3dhkleague.wixsite.com%2Fb3dhk2016&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b1f58ecc\" target=\"_blank\">http://ball3dhkleague.wixsite.com/b3dhk2016</a><br />\n<br />\nBall3D 香港玩家比賽入球片段 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw%2Fvideos&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dde2139a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw/videos</a><br />\n<br />\nBALL3D 巴西球王nak Skill &amp; Goal Compilation :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9bO57yXof10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9bO57yXof10&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0baef331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9bO57yXof10</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前多數逢晚上9點後都會有人開香港場，10點比較多人玩。歡迎新手入黎玩。只要你唔係惡意串人、下下屌鳩隊友個類人，我地願意帶住你玩。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為隻Game對初學者黎講太新鮮, 需較長時間掌握基本技術，建議新手得閒自行熟習玩法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家Maniek出咗3vs3 Bot，得閒想透過比賽黎練習又搵唔到人陪你玩可以係度自己單機練下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&emsp;<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"eb7138c0a2353e12884b6c5c4969457c37e6465d","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zsBeN2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzsBeN2Q.png&h=353c0eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>控制方法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nWASD = 上下左右移動<br />\n<br />\nMOUSE移動 = 控制視角<br />\n<br />\n左鍵 = 禁實蓄力 放開就會踢走個波<br />\n<br />\nSPACEBAR 空格/右鍵 = 跳躍 (需要用default setting先可以用spacebar及右鍵作跳躍)<br />\n<br />\nSHIFT = 挑高個波<br />\n<br />\nShift+A/D = 將個波撥向左方(A)/右方(D) (要蓄到Max power先用到，唔係嘅話只係普通shift)<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;E/mouse rotation = 拉西 (需要係Option較用Q/E或mouse控制)<br />\n<br />\nEsc = 去menu/離開房間/Option (圖入面個tab制功能廢咗，依家只可以用Esc開menu)<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"6218029ed77a9c4128ff5b3c700a5b1b3e1e2116","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>點樣同人傾計?</strong><br />\nEnter = 同所有人講野<br />\nbackspace(刪除鍵)/對話前加上/t = Team chat<br />\ntemplete: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/t</span></span>(空格)死球用plan D戰術、泊巴士死守完場等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新人一入黎隻Game會有tutorial教你玩，唔洗驚唔知點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面係香港球星HKBB拍嘅教學片(必睇):<br />\n<br />\n[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (1)移動人仔<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGXsD5iWAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoGXsD5iWAt4&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=cf02f384\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGXsD5iWAt4</a><br />\n<br />\n[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (2) 力度控制, 地波, CURVE<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD_xr_QxPmQ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrD_xr_QxPmQ%20&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2e0fefd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD_xr_QxPmQ </a><br />\n<br />\n[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (3) SHIFT (經過多次更新同改革，此教學未必完全適用)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efISzh2vYrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DefISzh2vYrY&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=75bcd02b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efISzh2vYrY</a><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"2c916caed0eae124ddf7688b265ba10fc846a0f8","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FAQ:</span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 建議新手一開始玩咩位置<br />\nA: 後防, 因為打後有多啲空間睇定黎用波, 同埋職責主要係做下清波閘波鳩放長波俾前鋒追等，加上我地有好多神龍幫手補鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，做後防唔會有好大壓力。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣加快傳波/射波時既球速?<br />\nA: 鬆開power制前跳一跳。以中短距離傳球為例, 如果齋禁power制傳波, 球速會比較慢, 較容易被對方截到波。而跳既幅度就會影響到粒波既軌跡<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣射波大力又唔會飛機?<br />\nA: 射波之前跳躍 就冇咁易飛機,因為同波既接觸面高左.可以控制跳躍時機去踢出地波/中腰波<br />\n跳到個波嘅中間就最貼地，跳得太低個波都會有少少離地（中腰波），跳得太高反而個波就會冇力<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解踢個波好似有DELAY咁?<br />\nA: 你一日禁實蓄力制 佢未爆POWER都唔會射個波出去 所以個波到既時候你就要放制射出去<br />\n<br />\nQ: 守門員好難做/好難擋波<br />\nA: 因為MOUSE左鍵係蓄力制 你可以係咁禁制 食一食個波 咁就唔會MISS左個波彈唔到。<br />\n禁實蓄力制 之後等個波到個陣放就可以撲走個波好遠。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 好難落西<br />\nA: 慣左射波跳躍個控制先 落西係BONUS野 只係射既時候加左Q/E制<br />\nQ:好難捉頂波timing<br />\nA:練多啲得架啦，同埋判斷個波個陣俾啲信心，基本上都係拋物線黎。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 隻game玩落都好撚lag喎<br />\nA: 一係網絡問題，可能係host間房(server) lag，又或者係你isp問題(e.g.某i-cable用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，可以係option到較antilag功能。<br />\n一係你部腦問題，熄咗個3D Grass、觀眾席同Anti Aliasing就得。<br />\n<br />\nCommand: 較球場背景 (禁Enter之後打段command就得)<br />\n/tribunes 0 &lt;&lt;冇人入場既球場<br />\n/tribunes 1 &lt;&lt;有約30000人入場既球場<br />\n/tribunes 2 &lt;&lt;乜都冇(大大提升流暢度)"},{"pid":"ff421ffe0c8f97ddcfd2e7eacc53132503ec605f","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Ball3DHK Moment</strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>個人比賽</strong><br />\n<br />\n第一屆1v1 Cup 冠軍: Player11s <br />\n第二屆1v1 Cup : (進行中)<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>團體比賽</strong><br />\n<br />\n第一屆聯賽(3vs3 賽制)冠軍: WFC (全季不敗)<br />\n<br />\n第二屆聯賽(4v4 賽制)冠軍: [-6] <br />\n神射手: [33] Ericsson (9球)<br />\n<br />\n第三屆聯賽(4v4 賽制)冠軍: =vMK= <br />\n神射手: =vMK= KiYoTaKe (13球)<br />\n<br />\n第一屆2vs2 Cup 冠軍: CGay - No0B + Chicken King<br />\n<br />\n同場加映: 絕殺入球<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sg1fSllNtrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsg1fSllNtrg&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5fa49630\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sg1fSllNtrg</a><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"f860bc3aaed521392e315baa2e4768bd7abceb27","tid":267674,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87da511016574a786e8b2922f77044d877c488ce","tid":267674,"uid":66217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:31:25.000Z","msg":"咩game黎"},{"pid":"fe4e55667e2ca0165adc5047286d96bf868fee16","tid":267674,"uid":43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:36:09.000Z","msg":"好似幾好玩"},{"pid":"94f18c1b4d1ca6df92acd3f424ca468eb71f8695","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩game黎</blockquote><br />\n第一身足球game <br />\n同普通足球game唔同嘅係 傳波射波控波頂波嘅timing要自己捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇得好似FIFA PES咁會幫你自動導航 捉錯timing有機會變超級大傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4016f008dfb17b43e7ce3121181d35ee4ec9d9","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"同埋隻game係免費+3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以跳黎跳去咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796992984e5656d5de40e37c5d359e80cd983dad","tid":267674,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score